#: src/components/tile.tsx:295
msgid "Day of the Dead"
msgstr "死者の日"

#: src/hooks/seasonal-events/day-of-the-dead.tsx:40
msgid "Day of the Dead is a celebration of life, memory, and the enduring bond between the living and those who have passed."
msgstr "死者の日は、生命と記憶、そして生者と亡き人々の間にある変わらぬ絆を祝う日です。"

#: src/components/tile.tsx:114
msgid "December"
msgstr "12月"

#: src/hooks/seasonal-events/christmas.tsx:85
msgid "Decorated trees, stockings, gift-giving, and shared meals now connect people across many climates and continents in a sense of home and continuity."
msgstr "飾り付けたツリーや靴下、贈り物、共に食卓を囲むことは、さまざまな気候や大陸にまたがって「家」と連続性の感覚を呼び起こします。"

