#: src/hooks/seasonal-events/eta-aquariids.tsx:115
msgid "The meteors are exceptionally fast and often leave long, delicate trains that linger in the sky."
msgstr "流星は非常に速く、長く繊細な光跡が空に残ることがよくあります。"

#: src/hooks/seasonal-events/geminids.tsx:125
msgid "The meteors are often bright and steady, tracing slow, colourful paths across the night."
msgstr "流星は明るく安定して見えることが多く、ゆっくりと色彩豊かな軌跡を夜空に描きます。"

